d 'LATINOBAROMETRO': module to load, standardize, and enrich a Latinobarometro survey wave
d
d      latinobarometro downloads (or reuses a cached copy of) a
d single year's Latinobarometro survey wave, loads the
d English-language    .dta file, sanitizes variable names and
d value-label names that are invalid in Stata (accented/Unicode
d characters and periods),    and optionally:	     1. renames
d every variable to a standardized name that is consistent across
d survey years, using the official	      Latinobarometro
d "Serie de Tiempo" crosswalk file, and        2. merges in World
d Bank total-population data by country and constructs a
d population-based sampling weight (wt_lac)	       suitable for
d pooled cross-country analysis. 
d
d KW: data management
d KW: latinobarometro
d
d Requires: Stata version 14
d
d Distribution-Date: 20260715
d
d Author: Jorge Soler-Lopez,  Bocconi University
d Support: email   jorge.solerlopez@@phd.unibocconi.it
d
f latinobarometro.ado
f latinobarometro.sthlp
